OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fcontinue to push northwards across the
OL,7,Fregion. It will be heavy and thundery
OL,8,Fat times, which could lead to some
OL,9,Fdifficult travelling conditions.
OL,10,FHowever, towards dawn, the rain should
OL,11,Fease for most. A mild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA cloudy start with patchy
OL,14,Frain in places. Brightening up, with
OL,15,Fsunny spells but also the risk of
OL,16,Fshowers developing. These likely to be
OL,17,Fheavy and thundery in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
