OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FShowers easing during Monday and
OL,7,FTuesday with sunnier spells emerging.
OL,8,FSimilar on Wednesday with variable
OL,9,Famounts of cloud, feeling fresher than
OL,10,Frecent days as temperatures fall away.
